Just go to src and run the make-script. In order to build you require the modules opengl, vrpn and vrg3d.

module load vrpn/7.33 opengl/nvidia-375.66 vrg3d/265 

You will also need to compile the tiletiff library in src/tiletiff. Simply run the make-script. No dependencies needed.



***** CAVE/YURT software *****
